information: The company NIEDERÖSTERREICHISCHE SAATBAUGENOSSENSCHAFT REGISTRIERTE GENOSSENSCHAFT MIT BESCHRÄNKTER H, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1927, which operates in the Bedding plants, bulbs and seeds industry. It is based in Windigsteig, Austria.
